high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bottle of wine on the green table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the table.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Place the knife in the pot on the left of the stove.
Pick up the pot on the left of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the wine bottle on the green table.
Place the pot behind the egg on the green table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a yellow handle knife in it on the green table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the stove, and then walk towards the middle of the green table to your left.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table.
Turn left and walk towards the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the left side.
Pick up the pan with the knife from the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the green table on your left.
Place the pan behind the egg on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the square pan with a yellow knife on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the counter then turn left, walk forward, and turn left to face the green table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the green table.
Walk to the stove.
Put the knife in the leftmost pot on the stove.
Pick up the leftmost pot on the stove.
Turn right and walk forward then turn left to face the green table.
Place the pot on the far side of the green table behind the egg.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a knife inside it on the green table by the egg.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk around to the far side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the closest large metal knife with a golden handle off of the kitchen island.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then turn right and walk up to the oven.
Put the large metal knife with a golden handle point down into the metal bowl on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal bowl with the knife in it that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then hang a left and walk up to the middle of the kitchen island.
Place the large metal bowl with the knife inside of it onto the kitchen island in front of the rightmost chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal bowl with a knife inside of it on the kitchen island.
